00:23:55,599 --> 00:23:57,239
Hurry, the lift is here.

443
00:23:57,439 --> 00:23:58,359
Coming.

444
00:23:58,479 --> 00:23:59,000
Hurry.

445
00:23:59,079 --> 00:24:00,079
