459
00:24:41,119 --> 00:24:42,280
Hello, senior.

460
00:24:42,520 --> 00:24:43,040
My name is...

461
00:24:43,160 --> 00:24:44,599
I don't care who you are.

462
00:24:44,760 --> 00:24:46,079
Stop following me.

463
00:24:46,319 --> 00:24:48,920
