00:25:15,079 --> 00:25:16,000
Congratulations.

476
00:25:16,239 --> 00:25:20,000
(You were the third person to my left.)

477
00:25:20,640 --> 00:25:22,479
(This was our first photo together.)

478
00:25:23,119 --> 00:25:25,040
(I will cherish it.)

