00:26:03,300 --> 00:26:04,940
♪And you want to go home♪

494
00:26:05,060 --> 00:26:08,013
♪I'm all alone on a deserted street♪

495
00:26:08,079 --> 00:26:09,319
(Jiang Yicheng,)

