546
00:27:33,119 --> 00:27:33,920
Wait!

547
00:27:34,119 --> 00:27:35,040
Thanks, Mum.

548
00:27:36,000 --> 00:27:36,760
You!

549
00:27:37,199 --> 00:27:37,680
